_:N10404858150e4ee0bbc7663de35e837f <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Gareth Davies was Exchequer Secretary to the Treasury between 21 April 2023 and 5 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>Previously, Gareth was appointed Parliamentary Private Secretary (PPS) to the Chancellor of the Exchequer in November 2022, and served on the House of Commons Finance Select Committee from 2019 and the Treasury Select Committee from 2021.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
